sac.graph

Class GraphSearchMonitor

  • java.lang.Object
    • sac.graph.GraphSearchMonitor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Runnable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ConsoleGraphSearchMonitor, GraphicalGraphSearchMonitor

    public abstract class GraphSearchMonitor
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Runnable
    Abstract monitor of graph search algorithm. Meant to be extended by displaying/logging classes suitable for given environment.
    Author:
    Przemysław Klęsk (wi.zut.edu.pl), Marcin Korzeń (wi.zut.edu.pl)
